    p
      br
    p I am currently working with clients who are looking for a home in your neighborhood.  My clients have seen many homes currently on the market, but none have fully met their needs and preferences.
    p
      br
    p In an effort to find other possibilities, I am reaching out to you, and other homeowners in the area, to help my clients find the right home.
    p
      br
