    p
      br
    p If you have a broker you prefer to work with, please have them contact me on your behalf, and I will gladly discuss the details with them.  My goal is to achieve a successful purchase for my clients that is mutually beneficial to all.
    p
      br
    p Thank you for your consideration of this inquiry.
    p
      br
    p Best Regards,
    p
      br
